#: ../source/changeStreams.txt:21
msgid "Change streams allow applications to access real-time data changes without the complexity and risk of tailing the :term:`oplog`. Applications can use change streams to subscribe to all data changes on a collection and immediately react to them."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/changeStreams.txt:28
